# HomeOnInternet вЂ” Architecture Overview

Personal site for Saumya Nayak built with **Next.js 13 Pages Router**, MDX blogs, Tailwind CSS, and a few external API integrations. No CMS layer вЂ” all content lives in code or MDX files.

---

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 13 (Pages Router вЂ” no App Router) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS 3 (`darkMode: 'selector'`) |
| Content (blog) | MDX via `@next/mdx` + `@mdx-js/loader` |
| Icons | `lucide-react` |
| Font | Google Fonts вЂ” Poppins (via `next/font/google`) |
| Route progress | `nprogress` |
| Sitemaps | `next-sitemap` |
| Deployment | Vercel |

