## Pages & Sections

| Route | File | Data source |
|-------|------|------------|
| `/` | `pages/index.js` | Static (inline) |
| `/projects` | `pages/projects.js` | `PROJECTS` array in `utils/constant.js` |
| `/work` | `pages/work.js` | `WORK` array in `utils/constant.js` |
| `/videos` | `pages/videos.js` | YouTube Data API v3 (`getStaticProps`) |
| `/blogs` | `pages/blogs.js` | `getAllPosts.js` (MDX) + Medium RSS via rss2json (`getStaticProps`) |
| `/blogs/<slug>` | `pages/blogs/<slug>/index.mdx` | MDX file (each exports `meta`) |
| `/reachme` | `pages/reachme.js` | Static social links |
| `/learnings` | `pages/learnings.js` | Placeholder вЂ” no nav link |

